OL,3,CWork to recruit thousands of new
OL,4,Cteachers underway by education
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FThe education secretary has today
OL,8,Fstarted work to recruit 6,500 new
OL,9,Fteachers as one of her first steps in
OL,10,Fthe job.
OL,12,FBridget Phillipson will write to all
OL,13,Feducation workforces to "make clear
OL,14,Fthe valuable role they will play in
OL,15,Fthis government's agenda for change",
OL,16,Fthe Department for Education said.
