OL,7,FLabour will reset "the government's
OL,8,Frelationship with the sector and
OL,9,Ftransforming the image of teaching -
OL,10,Fseen by the government as key to both
OL,11,Frecruiting new teachers and retaining
OL,12,Fthose already in classrooms", the
OL,13,Fdepartment added.
OL,15,FMs Phillipson will hold a reception
OL,16,Fwith key education stakeholders later
OL,17,Fthis week, as well as meeting with
OL,18,Fteaching unions in the coming days.
