OL,4,Cteachers underway by education
OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,FThe Department for Education will also
OL,8,Fresume and expand its teacher
OL,9,Frecruitment campaign, Every Lesson
OL,10,FShapes a Life, and will restart its
OL,11,Ffurther education recruitment
OL,12,Fcampaign, Share Your Skills.
OL,14,FThe announcement demonstrates the
OL,15,Fgovernment's "intent to re-establish
OL,16,Fteaching as an attractive, expert
OL,17,Fprofession, where the immeasurable
OL,18,Fimpact which teachers can make on
OL,19,Fchildren's lives is truly valued", the
OL,20,Fdepartment said.
