OL,7,FMs Phillipson said: "From day one, we
OL,8,Fare delivering the change this country
OL,9,Fdemands and putting education back at
OL,10,Fthe forefront of national life.
OL,12,F"We will work urgently to recruit
OL,13,Fthousands of brilliant new teachers
OL,14,Fand reset the relationship between
OL,15,Fgovernment and the education workforce.
