OL,5,Csecretary
OL,7,F"For too long the teaching profession
OL,8,Fhas been talked down, side-lined and
OL,9,Fdenigrated. I have made it my first
OL,10,Fpriority to write today to the people
OL,11,Fat the centre of making change happen:
OL,12,Four workforces.
OL,14,F"I want all children to have the best
OL,15,Flife chances which means recruiting
OL,16,Fand keeping great teachers in our
OL,17,Fclassrooms - today is the first step
OL,18,Fin that mission."
